## Interpreting the two-sample t-test

**Steps 6: make a conclusion**



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Save and tidy results
caff_test <- t.test(Taps ~ Group, 
                    data = CaffTaps, 
                    alternative = "greater")

tidy(caff_test, 
     conf.int = TRUE) %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  tab_options(table.font.size = 30)
```

